archon-bmad
===========

This project ports the implementation-automation pipeline of the BMAD Story
Automator onto the Archon workflow engine.

Derived from:

  bmad-automator (bmad-story-automator)
  https://github.com/bmad-code-org/bmad-automator
  Copyright (c) 2026 BMAD — MIT License

The adversarial code-review instructions inlined in
`workflows/archon-bmad-story-automator.yaml` (the `review` phase) are a paraphrased
derivative of the bundled `bmad-story-automator-review` skill from that
project. The per-story pipeline ordering (create -> dev -> auto -> review ->
commit, with per-epic retrospectives) and the "sprint-status.yaml is the
single source of truth" / "0 CRITICAL issues" completion gate are likewise
modeled on that project.

Designed for use with:

  BMAD-METHOD
  https://github.com/bmad-code-org/BMAD-METHOD
  MIT License

Built for:

  Archon
  https://archon.diy

